name: 101 Dalmatian Dog Puppy Tutu and Corset Halloween Costume or Christmas Gift 18M 2T 3T 4T 5 6 7 8
description:
This adorable set is for that animal lover in your life. It is cute, sassy and just plain fun! If you have a puppy themed birthday party, what better way to celebrate than to have the "top dog" sporting this set?


This set includes:

Full white tutu with black tulle polka dot spots & elastic waist. Removable dalmatian print tail.

Cotton dalmatian print corset top fully lined. Trimmed in red satin ribbons & red sequins. Fixed satin ribbon belt across waist.


My tutus are made with LOTS of very soft tulle. They have a comfortable elastic waist. The top is fully lined in satin or cotton if you choose, and the style of the top allows it to be adjustable for more wear as the little ones grow. I make all of these items myself. I enjoy doing custom orders, and depending on availability, will try my best to meet your wishes on just about any colors you want.


Also Available:

Snow White ~ Tinker Bell ~ Cinderella ~ Sleeping Beauty ~Witch ~

If your daughter has another character in mind, please feel free to ask about it!

Because of the nature of this custom item, there are no returns. However, I want you to be completely satisfied with your purchase, so if there is any concern, please let me know. I'm very easy to work with.


SHIPPING

Your custom outfit will be shipped within 7-14 days of payment being made. I'm glad to combine shipping to save you money. Insurance is optional but highly recommended, as I cannot be responsible for items once they have left my hands. No returns. Ships to the 50 United States ONLY.

PAYPAL PREFERED

Payment appreciated within 3 days of auction close. If you need longer to pay, just let me know.

USA SHIPPING ONLY!
